The paper discusses image retargeting techniques, which involves computer vision and graphics (cs.CV, cs.GR). The paper also mentions the growth of mobile communications and dynamic web page layouts, which suggests a focus on multimedia (cs.MM). The paper proposes a novel method of analyzing semantic information within the input image, which involves artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper mentions the need for retaining the meaning conveyed from the image, which suggests information retrieval (cs.IR).
